    <form method="post" id="fm1" class="form-login-container">

        <input type="hidden" id="nbAuthFailedAttemptsBeforeThisShot" value="" /><input type="hidden" id="nbMaxAttempts" value="" /><input type="hidden" id="lockTimeInSeconds" value="" /><section>

                       required name="username" value=""><div class="mdc-line-ripple"></div>
                <label for="username" class="mdc-floating-label">Adresse email</label>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section>
            <div class="mdc-text-field password-input mdc-text-field--with-trailing-icon">
                <i id="mdp-visibility" class="material-icons mdc-text-field__icon cursor-pointer mdp-visibility">visibility_off</i>
                <input type="password"
                       size="25"
                       tabindex="2"
                       accesskey="m"
                       autocomplete="current-password"
                       required
                       class="mdc-text-field__input"
                       id="password" name="password" value=""><div class="mdc-line-ripple"></div>

                </div>
        </section>

                    <div class="mdc-checkbox">
                      <input type="checkbox"
                             class="checkbox-stay-connect mdc-checkbox__native-control"

                             tabindex="5"
                             name="rememberMe"
                             id="rememberMe"/><div class="mdc-checkbox__background">

    <form method="post" id="passwordManagementForm">
        <input type="hidden" name="execution" value="bc02b5e6-99ef-4b4a-a842-cae69ed4c0d2_"/><input type="hidden" name="_eventId" value="resetPassword"/></form>

    <script type="text/javascript">
        var i = "Veuillez patienter..."
        $("#fm1").submit(function() {
            $(":submit").attr("disabled", true);
            $(":submit").attr("value", i);
            return true;
        });
        /*Affiche/masque le mot de passe*/
        document.getElementById( 'mdp-visibility' ).addEventListener( "click", function() {
            var passwordInput = document.getElementById('password');
            if (passwordInput.type === 'password') {
                this.innerHTML = 'visibility';
                passwordInput.setAttribute( 'type', 'text' );
            } else {
                this.innerHTML = 'visibility_off';
                passwordInput.setAttribute( 'type', 'password' );
            }
        });


        $(document).ready(function () {
            checkForMaxFailedLoginAttemptsMessages ()
            updateLockDurationLabel ()
        });
    </script>
